::DarkMouse::

She saw Quickstrike, Stingtra, Drillbit, KitKat, all ready to do 
battle.  She wondered if any of the others felt like they were on a 
suicide mission like she did.  She wished Scorponok would come to her 
side and tell her that he would fight by her and help her in the 
fight.  But she shook her head.  She knew that he no onger cared for 
her and she would have to fend for herself in this battle.

She marched along with the others towards the other Pred base.
She prayed to the matrix that she would make it out of this fight 
alive.
